item.title: How can i make my self lvl 126? ::master not working ::pure not working?
item.dc:creator: @Zeepwhat Zeepwhat
item.description:
@Zeepwhat wrote:

Ok this will probaly help alot.

  1. Open your Server folder.

2.From there find the “Characters” Folder.

3.Find your username.

4.Open it up.

You might have 2 options from here. (If you didn’t make yourself owner yet:
Scroll down until you find “Character rights” and 0. Change that 0 to a 3.
Save your work.
Then try ::master and ::pure, cause only admin+ usually can only do it.

Now the other option, If you are owner and is not working:
Scroll down to skills, Change the skills to 99 and the EXP to whatever.
Save your work.
And Log in and check to see if your stats are 99.

Hope this helps! Have fun!
